An MP from Narok has said Deputy President William Ruto is the best person to succeed President Uhuru Kenyatta in 2022. Narok Woman Representative Soipan Kudate said that God has already decided on the next leader who is DP Ruto and nobody can go against Lord’s wishes. “The next president will be a God-fearing man, who leads his people to development, peace and most of all the way to Lord,” said Soipan who spoke to the Star yesterday. She said that the Bible is clear that God will not allow his people to be attacked by their enemies whose plans is to see others people are not prospering in life and leadership “DP is a God-fearing man and many Kenyans are praying for him and God will not allow few individuals who are wishing him not to be the president of Kenya,” said she said. 